snippet.title: Insomnis :: Tráiler Anuncio PlayStation 5 (Inglés)
snippet.description:
#Insomnis is a first-person horror game based on exploration and puzzle solving.

In Insomnis, Joe Castevet has just inherited an old mansion on the outskirts of the country. What Joe didn't realize is that this legacy is actually a curse... Discover the dark secrets that await in the Castevet abode and fight against your own destiny in a story full of intrigue and terror!
